{"tid":1913414,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人可以講下點樣同異傾計講多啲嘢","createTime":"2020-03-06T18:31:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T23:17:05.000Z","uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b1c4b89d9feb70a416173a529f238f1849f28855","tid":1913414,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T18:31:39.000Z","msg":"毒撚唔識講嘢，好快end topic <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a1da2ef0971609bb2a4afad23b5031ef1b7fca","tid":1913414,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T18:34:27.000Z","msg":"講鹹野<br />\n<br />\n脫離支那是是香港唯一出路，但絕不能直接獨立，必須先經英美託管一段時間再經公投獨立<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1913061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1913061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n想消滅支那，我們就要帶領支畜暴動和革命，才有機會從內部瓦解支共（輸出革命+加速主義，缺一不可）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1911527\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1911527</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唔想香港淪為支那賤畜之境，大家必須肅清中資，整頓&ldquo;港漂&rdquo;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1902243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1902243</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n（國際戰線）借助日韓爆發武肺推動全球反奶共運動和全球排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cacc4458b0ad307a5ae8c59f73ff683cf6aa06a5","tid":1913414,"uid":264974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1c4b89d9feb70a416173a529f238f1849f28855","tid":1913414,"uid":81190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T18:31:39.000Z","msg":"毒撚唔識講嘢，好快end topic <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma